The Coffee House Sales Analysis Project focuses on analyzing sales data to understand customer behavior, product performance, and revenue trends. The project uses Excel-based analysis to generate insights that help improve sales strategy and business decision-making.
It includes data cleaning, pivot tables, dashboards, and visualizations to present key performance indicators clearly.

